title.narrative: National Trade Corridor Highway Investment Program, Tranche 2

description.narrative: The Project 2 (E35: Hasanabdal-Havellian Expressway) is part of the National Trade Corridor and the Central Asia Regional Economic Cooperation (CAREC) Corridor 5. It connects the existing Islamabad - Peshawar Motorway M1 near Hasanabadal to Havelian near Abbotabad.
